{"tid":648672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問，咩叫白話？","createTime":"2018-05-01T01:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T11:39:52.000Z","uid":53673,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3d95d388efb6bd5937cef89220cff4b43991935d","tid":648672,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"無知一問，成日聽到d大陸人話佢地識講/唔識講「白話」。白話即係廣東話？咁普通話係咪「黑話」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a6ac6b68c2d1f6bbeda28f606261b474459d98","tid":648672,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"白話文"},{"pid":"789acf54916ddbb4247a5367f8945b58926d3bc7","tid":648672,"uid":129509,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"你係咪大陸人？<br />\n白話=白話文<br />\n文言=文言文<br />\n你讀書老師冇教過？"},{"pid":"18c73c432ea372627283be59c11f8b50a3475cf9","tid":648672,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪大陸人？<br />\n白話=白話文<br />\n文言=文言文<br />\n你讀書老師冇教過？</blockquote><br />\n冇教過，白話文，文言文就識"},{"pid":"6c39bca396a05eb7902b692978e1200a0bbbe1b0","tid":648672,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"白話即係本地話，非專指粵語。<br />\n北京嘅白話咪普通話囉"},{"pid":"3d779de04d127c19e663aa9ed3f94d0addb6a98e","tid":648672,"uid":53673,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白話即係本地話，非專指粵語。<br />\n北京嘅白話咪普通話囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長知識了"},{"pid":"ab69f4ca9892fc5e3e246369444f80a17004dce4","tid":648672,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:08:49.000Z","msg":"我諗白話咪即係講嘢嘅說話囉, 我哋而家喺連登嘅大部分都係用緊白話你出字。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔用白話既話， 上邊個段野可能要咁寫<br />\n<br />\n我想白話等同平常人日常對話的用語， 而非書信上的用語 ， 我們連登日常的用語 亦都非常接近我們日常對話的用語， 亦是所謂 白話文。"},{"pid":"d7b491037a9758a9cd18709a461e9087e